      • serviceImmediately

        boolean serviceImmediately(ServiceRequest request)
        Check if the lift can be serviced immediately: 1. If the gate is open, current floor and direction is same as requested floor and direction, reopen the gate. 2. If the the lift is stationary and is present at the floor, just open the gate.
        Parameters:
        request - Request to be checked.
        Returns:
        true if the request matched the above criteria, false otherwise.
